msgctxt "Near_Raimei_001"
msgid "That helmet... Is it real?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "near00"
msgid "So tiiiired..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>*pant<2.pa> pant*<3.pa>\n"
"Babi's training is really tough, but...\n"
"\n"
"It's our fault the thieves were successful.\n"
"We have no room to complain."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: text_size
#. 4: text_size
msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Thanks to you bringing back the chief's\n"
"heirloom, we can finally take a break...\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>In theory, anyway. More likely, once we\n"
"finish repairing our spears, we'll have to\n"
"get started on more special training.\n"
"<3.te_si>*sigh* Babi's always got more special training...<4.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Babi is working way too hard, even\n"
"though the chief's heirloom is back!\n"
"\n"
"I hope I never become as intense\n"
"as her..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Thanks to your bringing back the chief's\n"
"heirloom, we can finally take a break.\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>The team over there is in a tizzy, though,\n"
"because Barta disappeared again.\n"
"\n"
"That kid is always going off by herself\n"
"and getting wrapped up in trouble..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: set_colour (grey)
#. 4: text_size
#. 5: text_size
#. 6: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm seriously glad that I'm not on the\n"
"same team as Barta.<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<3.se_co><4.te_si>I already have my hands full with "
"Babi...<5.te_si><6.re_co>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>From what I hear, you're the Hylian that\n"
"recovered the helm for the chief.\n"
"\n"
"It's a shame I didn't get to show those\n"
"thieves what I can do with my spear,\n"
"though.\n"
"<2.so>Anyway, maybe someday you and I can\n"
"get a little sparring in? We might both\n"
"learn something..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>From what I hear, you're the Hylian that\n"
"recovered the helm for the chief.\n"
"\n"
"Not only did you take care of the thieves,\n"
"but you also had the skill to calm the\n"
"Divine Beast...<2.pa>\n"
"<3.so>Anyway, maybe someday you and I can\n"
"get a little sparring in? I might really\n"
"learn something..."
msgstr ""

